    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Experts assess ACID properties when evaluating databases because they are critical for maintaining data integrity, especially in applications like banking or e-commerce where accuracy and reliability are paramount. While relational databases typically implement ACID fully, some NoSQL systems may relax these guarantees to achieve higher scalability and performance[4][6].",
